newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 2,162 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 2,162 contracts.

text.p: The Chicago Board of Trade Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totalled 2,162 contracts compared with 644 overnight Wednesday, according to the CBOT.
There were 134 wheat, 407 corn, 1,105 soybean, 201 soyoil, 274 soymeal, one corn call and 40 soybean options traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 1/4 to one cent lower, corn was 1/4 to 3/4 lower and soybeans were 1/4 to four cents lower.
